rComments: He is great at explaining, makes the material interesting to learn and has his bouts of humor here an there. Very knowledgeable professor, but be warned- His final exams are a massacre, so far I have taken 2 classes with him and is always the same- no matter how hard I study the final exam makes you wonder if you attended the right lecture.
THE FINAL EXAM IS TORTURE AT ITS FINEST.
exams are killer!! Even the midterm makes u rack your brain! The final is just MURDERRRR. He makes the material interesting but at the cost of brutalizing you in the lectures.
